snippet.title: Drowned Lake — Teaser
snippet.description:
Drowned Lake is a horror game that combines exploration with survival elements, with a full announcement coming later this year. Dredge out the Drowned Lake to find the secrets hidden in the murky waters!

Subscribe on X(Twitter) to learn more: https://twitter.com/Monumentallab
